modName: Stirling Shire Village - New Village In Skyrim
summary: This mod adds a new village to the west of Whiterun.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds a new village to the west of Whiterun.
Contains an Inn, a Store, A Blacksmith And 2 houses
There\'s A Horse
And Also A Powerful Sword, And A Book Of The Villages History.

Please comment and tell me how to improve my mods in the future

Bugs:
Village May Not spawn correctly when Fasttraveled to.
Follower Will Not Follow You Into Some Buildings

PS. The house textures will NOT look like this unless you run it with the Sexy Whiterun mod ( Which I Recommend Using )
author: G1fan1998
